The paper presents an active learning algorithm for classification, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm is applied to classification tasks, which are often related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the computational burden associated with maintaining version spaces, which is a topic in data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
